jdcal
=====

.. _TPM: http://www.sal.wisc.edu/~jwp/astro/tpm/tpm.html
.. _Jeffrey W. Percival: http://www.sal.wisc.edu/~jwp/
.. _IAU SOFA: http://www.iausofa.org/
